casebody.data:
Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation v. Landhold Corporation et al. (10522)

O’Connell, Norcott and Freedman, Js.

Argued March 25 decision released April 14, 1992 William H. Cashman, with whom, on the brief, was Tara L. Knight, for the appellant (named defendant). Barry K. Stevens, with whom, on the brief, was Matthew M. Hausman, for the appellee (plaintiff). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
